These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, alhambra, vegafina
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, spy, satire
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, zinnia, begonia
City: miami, san-francisco, london
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, hedgehog
3 different games are played: backgammon, canasta, billiard
 1. the person playing backgammon is the owner of the hamster##1
 2. the person playing billiard is the person who growsbegonia##1
 3. the vegafina-smoker is between the owner of the hedgehog and the alhambra-smoker##2
 4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 5. the person who growszinnia is the person watching satire movies##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 8. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Cigar      | alhambra    | vegafina   | pall-mall           |
| Movie-Genre          | spy       | satire    | action         |
| Hobby         | reading    | skydiving  | hiking        |
| Flower           | azalea | zinnia   | begonia      |
| City   | san-francisco        | london    | miami       |
| Pet   | hamster     | chinchilla  | hedgehog       |
| Game         | backgammon     | canasta | billiard |

