There are 3 different nationalities: australian, british, dutch
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, may, june
3 different games are played: canasta, scrabble, go
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is the british##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 4. the person playing canasta is between the person driving the train and the person driving the car##2
 5. the dutch is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the train is the person traveling to new-york##1
 7. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person playing go##1
 8. the old-henry-smoker is the person who's hobby is writing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Transport      | car   | van    | train         |
