3 different games are played: bridge, snooker, domino
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, marigold, rose
There 3 different types of food: apple, broccoli, pineapple
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, soccer, water-polo
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, yellow, pink
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is in the middle##1
 2. the coach is in the middle##1
 3. the person who growsrose is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
 4. the fan of trance is the person playing snooker##1
 5. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 6. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 7. the person who likes pink is between the firefighter and the person who growstulip##2
 8. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 9. the person playing snooker is the person who likes aquamarine##1
10. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
11. the person who likes aquamarine is the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Job      | firefighter | coach      | mechanic      |
| Music-Genre         | dubstep     | soul     | trance  |
| Game   | domino | bridge  | snooker |
| Flower   | marigold  | rose     | tulip |
| Food           | apple        | pineapple | broccoli     |
| Sport         | handball    | water-polo | soccer   |
| Color     | yellow        | pink        | aquamarine   |

