.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
3 different games are played: bridge, chess, billiard
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, aristoff, bolivar
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, may, march
City: berlin, prague, edinburgh
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, bridgesy, mystery
House: colonial, cape-cod, modern
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, light-blue, lilac
1. the person playing chess is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
2. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
4. the colonial house is between the person watching epic movies and the person traveling to prague##2
5. the bolivar-smoker is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person who's birthday is in march##2
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
7. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person playing chess##1
8. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
9. the person watching bridgesy movies is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Game      | bridge      | chess      | billiard       |
| Cigar          | aristoff      | bolivar    | davidoff   |
| Birthday         | march    | november     | may     |
| City           | prague    | berlin | edinburgh   |
| Movie-Genre   | bridgesy    | mystery    | epic       |
| House         | modern | colonial      | cape-cod    |
| Color     | light-blue       | blood-red | lilac |

