The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, october, september
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, dunhill, havana
3 different pets are kept: lizard, guinea-pig, hedgehog
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, scientist, project-manager
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, nigerian, spanish
1. the nigerian is the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the scientist is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the project-manager is on the right of the scientist##1
4. the havana-smoker is on the right of the spanish##1
5. the tower house is between the person drinking fanta and the person who's birthday is in april##2
6. the colonial house is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
8. the colombian is the havana-smoker##1
9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
