The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, sunflower, tulip
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, siglo, alhambra
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cycling
City: miami, colone, san-francisco
1. the person watching spy movies is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person watching disaster movies and the alhambra-smoker##2
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
5. the game-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
7. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
8. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1
9. the person who growssunflower is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person traveling to miami##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Movie-Genre      | fantasy    | spy       | disaster      |
| Hobby          | woodworking   | hiking   | puzzles  |
| Birthday           | october  | may | march    |
| Flower   | amaryllis   | sunflower     | tulip  |
| Cigar           | alhambra     | game        | siglo |
| Sport         | basketball | baseball   | cycling  |
| City     | colone    | san-francisco     | miami      |

 